### Out of scope

- Reordering the queue mid-cascade (drag handles in the dialog).
- Skipping the current issue without aborting (would need a new action).
- Cross-project bulk YOLOs.
- Worktree-based parallelism (separate primitive; bulk YOLO is intentionally serial).

